1. Decide what type of pizza you want
2. Decide how many pizzas we want
3. Decide how many beer we want
4. Call the pizza place
    a. they answered - go to step 5
    b. they dont answer - go to step 4 again 
5. Place the order 
    a. pay over phone - see step 6
    b. pay at door - wait/ skip to step 7
6. Give credit card information 
7. Wait 
8. Answer the door
    a. pay at door - see step 9
9. take pizza